videos.description: Kansas' Udoka Azubuike sets the hard, but legal screen, causing a collision with Justin Gray. Gray would need assistance leaving the court to the bench.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Gray injured on pick-and-roll collision

videos.description: Kansas jumps to a 13-7 lead in the first half after Devonte' Graham drills a corner triple.
videos.headline: Graham hits corner 3 as Kansas takes early lead

videos.description: The Texas Tech crowd calls for a travel, and Kansas sharpshooter Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk silences them with a 3.
videos.headline: Red Raiders fans want travel, get Jayhawks 3

videos.description: Kansas' Devonte' Graham drives and lobs it to Udoka Azubuike who throws down as the Jayhawks lead the Red Raiders 25-20.
videos.headline: Graham connects with Azubuike for electric oop

videos.description: Texas Tech's Zhaire Smith defies gravity to get the tip-in around a swarm of Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Smith almost hits head on rim

videos.description: Marcus Garrett drives down the lane and absolutely launches for a one-hand tomahawk jam.
videos.headline: Garrett erupts for #SCTop10 dunk

videos.description: Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk hits his fourth 3-pointer of the night, getting a friendly bounce off the iron.
videos.headline: Mykhailiuk gets shooter's bounce

videos.description: Keenen Evans shows great vision to lead Norense Odiase to the basket for a layup.
videos.headline: Evans' smooth assist sets up Red Raiders' layup

videos.description: Zhaire Smith throws up the delicate floater but Udoka Azubuike spikes it like a volleyball for the block.
videos.headline: Red Raiders not allowed in Azubuike's paint

videos.description: No one can keep up with Texas Tech's Keenan Evans as he darts to the rim and hits the tough layup in traffic.
videos.headline: Evans zips down court for impressive finish

videos.description: Devonte' Graham navigates through the lane and initiates contact for the hoop and harm.
videos.headline: Graham controls body for and-1 finish

videos.description: Jarrett Culver gets the rebound and takes it all the way himself for the two-handed jam over Mitch Lightfoot.
videos.headline: Culver goes coast-to-coast for posterizing slam

videos.description: Devonte' Graham fires a cross-court bounce pass to Malik Newman for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Beautiful bounce pass sets up Kansas triple
TTU VS KU

videos.description: Texas Tech trails Kansas 67-64 after Jarrett Culver shoots the 3 without hesitation.
videos.headline: Culver keeps Red Raiders alive with cold-blooded triple

videos.description: Zhaire Smith is playing the entire game above the rim with a crazy display of athleticism on the putback finish to tie the game at 68-68.
videos.headline: Texas Tech ties it on insane Smith putback

videos.description: Devonte' Graham has a wide-open dunk under the basket but Zhaire Smith flashes in to get the block and keep the game tied.
videos.headline: Smith delivers on D with huge block

videos.description: Devonte' Graham gets to his spot and sinks the clutch jumper to give the Jayhawks a 70-68 lead.
videos.headline: Kansas regains lead on clutch Graham jumper

videos.description: Devonte' Graham does it all himself on the drive with an acrobatic finish to put the Jayhawks up 72-68 with under a minute left.
videos.headline: Graham's prayer falls to extend Kansas lead

videos.description: Devonte' Graham hit clutch shot after clutch shot in the 2nd half, saying he "just wanted to win" and had to stay aggressive.
videos.headline: Graham the star as Kansas holds on
